snippet.title: OrbusVR Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
OrbusVR is a new VR MMORPG developed from the ground-up for room-scale virtual reality systems including the HTC Vive and Oculus Rift + Touch. It launches into Early Access on December 15th. More info: http://orbusvr.com

(Updated trailer featuring footage from World Boss fight!)
